      <p>.NET Developer | Animator | Content Creator</p>
      <p>Passionate about coding, automation, and storytelling.</p>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/davinceleecode/" target="_blank">Linkedin</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/davinceleecode" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/users/3064448/davinceleecode" target="_blank">Stack Overflow</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
